The environment variable, LD_LIBRARY_PATH, must be defined in  order 
to use this version of Smokeview on a Linux system.  This variable 
must point to  the  location of the shared library, libimf.so, included
with this  distribution.  If you are running the csh or tcsh shell then
you may add the following line
 
setenv LD_LIBRARY_PATH ~/LIBS

in your local .cshrc  file.  Make sure you create a directory named LIBS and copy
copy libimf.so into it. 

